text.name: SQL
text.data:
CREATE TABLE "schueler" (
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL UNIQUE,
 "vorname" TEXT NOT NULL,
 "nachname" TEXT NOT NULL,
 "geburtsdatum" TEXT,
 "klasse_id" INTEGER NOT NULL,
 PRIMARY KEY("id" AUTOINCREMENT),
 FOREIGN KEY("klasse_id") REFERENCES "klassen"("id")
);
